textfsm_template:
Value MROUTE_SOURCE (\S+)
Value GRP (\S+)
Value UPTIME (\S+)
Value EXPIRES (\S+)
Value RP (\S+)
Value FLAGS (\S+)
Value RPF_NBR (\S+)
Value INCOMING_INTERFACE (\S+)

Start
  # Matches lines with (*, G)
  ^\(\*\s*,\s*${GRP}\),\s*uptime:\s*${UPTIME},\s*expires:\s*${EXPIRES},\s*RP:\s*${RP},\s*flags:\s*${FLAGS},\s*RPF\s*nbr:\s*${RPF_NBR}\s*$$ -> More
  # Matches lines with (S, G)
  ^\(${MROUTE_SOURCE},\s*${GRP}\),\s*uptime:\s*${UPTIME},\s*expires:\s*${EXPIRES},\s*RP:\s*${RP},\s*flags:\s*${FLAGS},\s*RPF\s*nbr:\s*${RPF_NBR}\s*$$ -> More

More
  ^\s*Incoming\s*interface:\s*${INCOMING_INTERFACE},\s*RPF\s*nbr:\s*${RPF_NBR}$$ -> Record
